name: Die Legende von den Drachenrittern - Jaina

description: Higher, further, faster, more! That's the daring new attitude of Earth's Mightiest Hero, Captain Marvel! As Carol Danvers comes to a crossroads in her life, she makes a dramatic decision that will alter the course of everything. But when she heads into space, Carol lands in the middle of a galactic uprising! And taking her cat with her seemed like a good idea at the time, but there's more to Chewie than meets the eye - unless you're Rocket Raccoon, Carol's new ally in the Guardians of the Galaxy! Plus: When a bad guy she has history with tries to blackmail her - and turn the Avengers against her - it's payback time! Captain Marvel's mighty adventures continue as she shows how to win friends and influence people of all species! Collecting CAPTAIN MARVEL (2014) #1-11.
name: Volume 3

description: Comic Shop News is comics' weekly newsletter. Each issue is full-color, 8-12 pages in length, and features CSNsider, news, and interviews. CSN has a complete monthly checklist (complete with PREVIEWS order numbers), plus exclusive CSN Hot Picks, 'Fab Firsts,' and a monthly checklist of all the first issues for the month!

In the shadow of Wayne Manor, Shazam and Black Adam are duking it out, while deep underground, Batman and his allies have unearthed the ultimate weapon against Superman from its hiding place. But just as Batman begins to believe he may be able to turn the tide, two of Superman’s allies burst into the Batcave and attack! Has the Resistance come this far just to lose again?

It's finally here - the second collection of Irwin Allen's classic LOST IN SPACE, brought to comics! Based on the unfilmed episode "Malice in Wonderland", this hardcover collects Issues 4-6 of THE LOST ADVENTURES and includes original script pages, line art, and other exclusive goodies!

Note: The digital edition (2/15/2017) for this volume was released before the print edition.
name: Volume Two

volume.name: Irwin Allen's Lost In Space: The Lost Adventures: Malice in Wonderland

description: Cuba, capital of the new economic empire, in the year 2082. Beautiful Morea Doloniac is an ordinary employee in one of the biggest meta-national companies on the planet, the DWC. She is only a vague relation to the founder of the company, Nathan Doloniac. One day, she is nearly killed when commando squads execute, everywhere on the planet, members of her family. As the only survivor, she finds herself at the head of one of the main economic powers of the XXIth century. More mysterious, the attempt on her life was a success... She died... And yet, she is still alive! She is the toy of two factions, which have been manipulating humanity for centuries - the Angels and the Dragons, who possess powers beyond what man is able to imagine…
name: Angels' Blood

description: As Brian Michael Bendis' New Avengers roster is completed, who is the masked Ronin - and why has Captain America recruited this mysterious figure? In the wake of the tumultuous events of HOUSE OF M, a new threat emerges that may be impossible to stop. Canada's premier super-team finds that out the hard way - will the Avengers fare any better? And when CIVIL WAR breaks out across the Marvel Universe, Iron Man and Captain America will find themselves on opposite sides - and their team will be torn in two! Plus: Whose side is Spider-Woman on? Luke Cage marries Jessica Jones! A military rarity! And the Illuminati's introduction! Collecting NEW AVENGERS (2004) #11-25, NEW AVENGERS: CUSTOM #676 - ARMY & AIR FORCE, GIANT-SIZE SPIDER-WOMAN #1, NEW AVENGERS ANNUAL (2006) #1, NEW AVENGERS: ILLUMINATI (2006) ONE-SHOT and CIVIL WAR: THE CONFESSION.
name: Volume 2

volume.name: New Avengers by Brian Michael Bendis: The Complete Collection

description:
With the realities of the world crashing in around him, Robert Moore struggles to accept the truth that he is actually a robotic assassin built by the CIA for covert missions and assassinations. He refuses his first mission in his self-aware state, but when he learns of the global ramifications of inaction, Robert must choose between compromising his morals or facing the consequences of his decision.

Note: The digital edition (2/15/2017) for this issue was released before the print edition.
The laziest girl in the world is given the ultimate task in the universe in this hilarious origin story.

volume.name: True Believers: Wolverine: Enemy of the State

description: Vampire death dealer Selene continues her struggle against the Lycan clan and the Vampire faction that betrayed her, with both sides trying to use the blood of her and her daughter to become Corvinus Strain hybrids. After hiding her daughter, Selene attempts to end the eternal war between Lycans and Vampires, though she must take a risk that may cost her her life.

Selene and her progeny David, son of a vampire coven leader, escape the relentless pursuit of Lycan soldiers under orders by their new leader, Marius. However, they are soon found by the Corvinus Coven. But instead of violence, they are offered a truce by their new vampire

Elder, Semira. In return, Selene, the greatest of Death Dealers, is welcomed as a mentor to train the vampire ranks. But unfortunately, she is mysteriously poisoned for reasons unknown and it seems as if all is not well within the Council of Corvinus.

In order to save Selene's life from bloodletting, David spirits her away from the Corvinus Coven, seeking sanctuary with another coven of vampires in the Arctic north that does not engage in the war. Meanwhile, Marius' mole inside the vampire coven, a beautiful Death Dealer by the name of Alexia, provides him with the location of Selene and David's destination. As the Lycans converge on the Nordic Coven, David discovers the true nature of his origins...that his mother was the Highborn Vampire Elder, Amelia.

Marius and his Lycan soldiers have breached the Nordic vampires stronghold and are poised to destroy them as well. While trying her best to protect this sacred coven, Selene is brutally attacked and gravely wounded by Marius and Alexia. Now, she lies at the very threshold of death's door with no hope for salvation...
